      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for gdk-pixbuf fixes the following issue:\n\n- CVE-2026-5201: improper validation of color component counts when processing a specially crafted JPEG image can lead\n  to a heap buffer overflow (bsc#1261210).\n",
